		Chopping blocks are the foundation of the serious woodsmans set of workstations. This workstation provides an improvement in the effectiveness of your tools. Work performed on a chopping block is generally faster than on the ground.

		In addition, there may be certain recipes that can only be performed with the help of a chopping block. For those intending to work with large amounts of wood, it should be the first workstation you acquire.
